name: Colonel Feyn Gospic (V)
Lore: 'One of General Dodonna''s chief strategic advisors. Planned the Rebel fleet''s approach to the Death Star.',
Text: 'While Massassi Base Operations on table, opponent may deploy only one Imperial to each Yavin 4 site per turn. Doubles Rebel Tech bonus to Attack Run. Once per turn, may take Balanced Attack or a commander into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
